flavor_text_entries.flavor_text:
It makes its nest by damming
streams with bark and mud. It is
known as an industrious worker.

While its movements out of water
are sluggish, it can swim as fast
as any FEEBAS.

A river dammed by BIBAREL will
never overflow its banks, which
is appreciated by people nearby.

It busily makes its nest with
stacks of branches and roots it
has cut up with its sharp incisors.

It busily makes its nest with
stacks of branches and roots it
has cut up with its sharp incisors.

Les digues insubmersibles qu’il
construit font le bonheur des
habitants proches.

するどい　まえばで　けずりとった
きのえだや　ねっこを　つみあげて
みずべに　せっせと　すを　つくる。

예리한 앞니로 갉아 얻은
나뭇가지나 뿌리를 쌓아
물가에 부지런히 보금자리를 만든다.

Il tranche les branches et les racines de ses incisives
aiguisées pour construire des barrages.

Emsig durchbeißt es mit seinen scharfen Vorderzähnen
Wurzeln und Äste und baut daraus sein Nest.

Con sus incisivos roe ramas y raíces y las apila para
construir sus madrigueras junto al río.

Costruisce con zelo la tana in riva ai corsi d’acqua,
levigando radici e rami con gli affilati incisivi.

It busily makes its nest with stacks of branches and
roots it has cut up with its sharp incisors.

鋭い　前歯で　削り取った
木の枝や　根っこを　積み上げて
水辺に　せっせと　巣を　作る。

かわを　きのみきや　どろの　ダムで
せきとめて　すみかを　つくる。
はたらきものとして　しられている。

강을 나무줄기나 진흙의 댐으로
막아서 거처를 만든다.
부지런한 일꾼으로 알려져 있다.

Il construit des barrages de boue et d’écorce le long
des fleuves. C’est un ouvrier de renom.

Es baut sein Nest, indem es in Flüssen Dämme aus
Schlamm und Ästen baut. Ein fleißiger Arbeiter.

Para anidar, crea presas en los ríos con maderas y
barro. Tiene fama de trabajador.

Sbarra il corso dei fiumi con corteccia e fango per
farsi la tana. È noto come lavoratore instancabile.
